Generic single-database configuration with async SQLAlchemy support.

Usage:
------

# Generate a new migration after model changes:
cd code
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Description of changes"

# Apply all pending migrations:
alembic upgrade head

# Downgrade one revision:
alembic downgrade -1

# Show current revision:
alembic current

# Show migration history:
alembic history

Note: The database URL is configured via the DATABASE_URL environment variable.
If not set, it defaults to SQLite at ./voicechat.db
